        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3490643689" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8803319216446465409">Fantastic second volume of Caro’s biography of Lyndon Johnson, including the controversial and nail-biting Senate campaign in 1948. Caro not only focuses on Johnson, but also brilliantly describes the political climate and historical context. (The Years of Lyndon Johnson, Part II.)</span>

          </span>
        </div>


