<li class='cover' id='bookCover_86524'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/86524.The_Path_to_Power"><img alt="The Path to Power" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1349023045l/86524._SX50_.jpg" />
